nodes.text: Colonel Feyn Gospic was a male Human in the service of the Rebel Alliance in 0 BBY, acting as one of the chief strategic advisors to General Jan Dodonna. During the Battle of Yavin, he was present in the Rebel base on Yavin 4. He developed the strategy for the Rebel fighters that was used for the attack approach to the first Death Star. Gospic used the OrC-19 com-scan integrator console to follow the Battle of Yavin, and was attracted to the Force without knowing it.
